"P800262832" "Reconsider your options."
// ContactRequiresText :
"P3611273721" "You are of the wrong alignment to get this tip."
// IDontKnowYouString :
"P2659787689" "You're unsure of exactly what to do with this information"
// NoTasksRemainingString :
"P3469732091" "This tip is of no use to you."
// PlayerBusyString :
