// Page VillainOrRogue Text :
"P3448748413" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Stuttered Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a radio on the ground with a message playing over and over. It appears to be a plea for help. You listen in...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>S-s-somebody, anybody, p-p-please help me! My n-n-name is Steven Werner, I am on the run from the Family. They're after me for v-v-v...various reasons that I cannot get into. R-r-regardless, a capo named Paulie "The Gun Show" Morrini is out for my b-b-blood.<br> <br>I will pay whoever helps me top d-d-dollar to take down Paulie and his goons - whatever you want, you've g-g-got it! <br><br></scale></color></font>It seems like another rich person in the Isles is on the run from the Family. You've heard of Steven Werner - he deals in high priced magical artifacts, frequently traded in Sharkhead Isle, meaning that he has more money than he knows what to do with. Some say he frequently gives these artifacts to help out heroes in Paragon City. Whatever artifact the Family is after, it must be important. <br><br>Getting the Family off of his case would equal a large payday and perhaps access to his secret collections. However, storming where he is currently hiding would allow you access to whatever item he's hiding from the Family."
// Answer Text :
"P1065815467" "VILLAIN: Find Steven Werner and take whatever he's hiding for yourself!"
// Answer Text :
"P2548759177" "ROGUE: Track down Paulie "The Gun Show" Morrini to help Steven Werner - for the right price."
// Page Vigilante Text :
"P2556820240" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Stuttered Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a radio on the ground with a message playing over and over. It appears to be a plea for help. You listen in...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>S-s-somebody, anybody, p-p-please help me! My n-n-name is Steven Werner, I am on the run from the Family. They're after me for v-v-v...various reasons that I cannot get into. R-r-regardless, a capo named Paulie "The Gun Show" Morrini is out for my b-b-blood.<br> <br>I will pay whoever helps me top d-d-dollar to take down Paulie and his goons - whatever you want, you've g-g-got it! <br><br></scale></color></font>More scum in the Isles hunting other scum - business as usual here. As far as you're concerned, none of them deserve to be saved. Not even this Steven Werner, who supposedly sells his artifacts for heroes to use. <br><br> But how does he get those artifacts? And <i>who</i> does he give them to? Anyone who can actually <i>use</i> them? Of course not, he probably just helps supply all those heroes who are too caught up in themselves to get what's <i>really</i> needed done. <br><br> But this item that Werner has...it's probably powerful. <i>Really</i> powerful if he's willing to offer everything for it. This could be - no, it <i>is</i> something you could <color red>use for yourself.</color> To show the people of Paragon and the Isles what happens when someone knows how to wield TRUE power!"
// Answer Text :
"P1799181336" "VILLAIN: Find Steven Werner and take whatever he has for yourself!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


