// Page VillainOrRogue Text :
"P1941275207" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>After interrogating one of your victims, you discovered something of interest.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Your victim broke down and talked.  It wasn't what you were hoping for, but you discovered that a large force of Wyvern agents stepped over some boundaries.  They are holding a very powerful Arachnos dignitary hostage in an Arachnos base nearby.  They've made threats to kill him unless their demands are met.</scale></color></font><br> <br>This presents you with the perfect opportunity to teach Wyvern a lesson.  Their base of operations will be vulnerable with such a large force deployed.  You could very easily break into their hideouts in the area and with the help of some explosives blow the place to kingdom come.<br><br>On the other hand, you could 'liberate' the Arachnos dignitary--for a price--and earn favor with Arachnos all in one fell swoop!"
// Answer Text :
"P1779760615" "VILLAIN: Destroy the vulnerable Wyvern hideout!"
// Answer Text :
"P3815268247" "ROGUE: Liberate the kidnapped Arachnos Dignitary for a price."
// Page Vigilante Text :
"P2690092898" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>After interrogating one of your victims, you discovered something of interest.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Your victim broke down and talked.  It wasn't what you were hoping for, but you discovered that a large force of Wyvern agents stepped over some boundaries.  They are holding a very powerful Arachnos dignitary hostage in an Arachnos base nearby.  They've made threats to kill him unless their demands are met.<br> <br>This presents you with the perfect opportunity to teach Wyvern a lesson.  Their base of operations will be vulnerable with such a large force deployed.  You could very easily break into their hideouts in the area and with the help of some explosives blow the place to kingdom come."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

